Balaji is a PhD candidate enrolled in the Regulatory Biology program with a specialization in Cellular and Molecular Medicine. He is completing his dissertation research in the laboratory of Dr. Hannelore Heemers at the Department of Cancer Biology, Lerner Research Institute, Cleveland Clinic. 
